Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.88,0:00:23.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.43,0:00:29.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.31,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.52,0:00:43.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然  充滿疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.69,0:00:51.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友一起度過每一天 直到將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.95,0:00:58.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流著眼淚  無法釋懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.71,0:01:09.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想請教  如何追回失去的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.76,0:01:16.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上擷取你的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著舞動的燈光  至今無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.06,0:01:28.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ahh  去把謎團解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.24,0:01:33.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把謎團解開吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.21,0:21:51.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜言蜜語說一整晚說不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.34,0:21:55.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不覺得累  all night long
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.55,0:22:03.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連戀愛的空閒都沒有  事情如波濤洶湧般襲來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.70,0:22:12.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在記憶中游泳 現實總是 cool and dry
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.19,0:22:19.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要確認這份愛情  我該往哪裡徘徊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.24,0:22:27.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如遠方的雲  想要追隨無法掌握的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.09,0:22:36.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時何處  內心發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.18,0:22:40.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使完全瞭解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.35,0:22:44.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會永遠喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.48,0:22:52.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管每天生活在戰鬥的日子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.68,0:23:00.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會想起懷念的故鄉  浮現從前的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.83,0:23:07.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求著  光與影的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛逝的秒針 不斷流動的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今社會人心乾涸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破案的推理能將之灌溉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天故事發生在莊嚴的電影世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怪獸的偽裝下事件因而發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.81,0:00:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大怪獸哥梅拉殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.32,0:01:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.79,0:02:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真正的哥梅拉耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是名不虛傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它好強喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠 好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子就是要來這裡見習的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的一個老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.89,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哥梅拉的生父 三上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小朋友們多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？ 想不想靠近點看看哥梅拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.24,0:02:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在開始我們會暫時休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓你們看一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.18,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些大樓好小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉的背竟然破掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉裡面生出了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他穿著哥梅拉的服裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.95,0:02:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在這個迷你城市裡作亂 好讓攝影機拍攝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這些大樓做得還真是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂來 可惡的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少用你們的髒手亂摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把佈景弄壞的話 我可不會善罷干休啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演 你也想點辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.86,0:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這些小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這樣吧 還是讓我來照顧這些小朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我今天下午也沒什麼戲要拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了 松井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥梅拉是人類最好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.43,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每一次會讓哥梅拉引起暴動的都是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這個時候能需壓住情緒激動的哥梅拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我小精靈艾梅拉了 小朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅拉不就是那個到危急關頭才會現身的戒指精靈嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.29,0:03:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾梅拉的身體明明只有這麼小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她的臉好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她也太老了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.17,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說完了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些工作人員真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很愛哥梅拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這群人十年來跟哥梅拉攜手同心像個大家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也只能到今年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些怪獸電影怎麼說都是騙小朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就不流行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些音樂也都播到爛了 而每次又是同樣的模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一場戲的佈景跟特殊效果卻費用不低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連當年出道只有十四歲的小精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也二十四歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就已經落伍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.44,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 昨天拍好的片子現在都已經沖洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以一起到試映室裡面去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龜井製作人你不一起去看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 友美 一起去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你談談那件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 那件事就不需要談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說的是什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是下一部電影的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他問我要不要扮演一位女刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像他這麼口無遮攔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧他能說得出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不錯了 接下來的工作有著落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我們飯碗差不多要丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？ 阿松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.68,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也來找我演下一部電影的兇手角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 只有我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我們快點到試映室裡欣賞哥梅拉的英姿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼松井 這些小孩就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 這裡有好多怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是曾經被哥梅拉打倒過的怪獸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒想到會把妳嚇成這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻手是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哥梅拉的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門在特寫的時候用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有利用遙控控制的哥梅拉的頭部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.63,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我去把它拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後哥梅拉的電影是不是真的不拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼有趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是好像要花好多錢的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是花在飼料上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉那麼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小鬼真是夠笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才哥梅拉到了這個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後拿刀把我刺傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它現在到哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從門那裡逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 小朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可以看到攝影棚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在那邊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是剛才那個製作人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是松井嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.67,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了 他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是從那扇門逃跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你們怎麼會在這裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到哥梅拉沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才跟它撞到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那…那不是松井嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看到哥梅拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.00,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有可以讓它藏身的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是騰空飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 哥梅拉什麼時候會飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到地上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 會是自殺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.63,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上午十一點半左右凶案發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都在什麼地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我一個人在攝影棚一樓的房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區分鏡頭的最後確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你就沒有證人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演伯伯 你流了好多汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常就很容易流汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在你進入道具倉庫的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手已經把哥梅拉的道具服穿上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且就站在這裡了對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才已經幫他緊急處理過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點送到醫院比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的腳這樣是不可能犯罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪口小姐在事件發生的時候 妳為什麼會在這裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.00,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想哥梅拉電影的結局既然決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想請龜井導演一起來看看毛片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得效果還是拍得蠻不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拍好之後還沒有經過編修的電影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 沒想到就碰到這樣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友美姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿哥梅拉服裝的兇手背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有看到吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有看到裡面是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只注意到他跑起來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.94,0:09:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑的樣子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑得很困難的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不習慣穿那身衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡除了松井之外誰都沒有穿過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.39,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說松井先生、阪口小姐還有三上導演這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都在試映室裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那個時候我也在看毛片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿笠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是住在新一家隔壁的那個天才博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久仰大名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你常常會創造出一些奇怪的發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.83,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 所有的工作人員都在試映室裡面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途離開的只有她一個人而己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過想想那個時候就好像有一個人也出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這個人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.37,0:09:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說嘛 我真的不知道這桶油漆是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道今天下午就要拍戲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能在佈景裡面放桶油漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是中途離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了毛片以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然在這個佈景裡面發現了一些需要調整的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會懷疑龜井製作人是我殺的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是安達先生出去的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有四、五分鐘而己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在四、五分鐘之內穿上道具服殺一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再順著樓梯上去回到試映室裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就時間上來說根本不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會是誰會把油漆擺在這個地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把油漆放在那裡的不是安達先生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看嘛 我們上午把戲排演完之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.87,0:10:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然完全不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.92,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼松井先生不一起看毛片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.56,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前找他來看他都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.12,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他早就說過不願意再演哥梅拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井先生他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近一直跟龜井製作人透露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉已經演不下去了 想演一些普通的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼也想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個兇手到底消失到哪去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個轉過來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直沿著腳印到了樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.96,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來替哥梅拉做一個墳墓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後他就從屋頂上的門跑到外面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南…做墳墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 現在不是談那種事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要像哥梅拉一樣生氣啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像哥梅拉一樣生氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.14,0:11:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樓梯上沒有尾巴的印子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是哥梅拉生氣了上樓梯的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉每次生氣 它的尾巴就會翹起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.09,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 我已經知道兇手的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我不能到這個攝影棚裡面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可不是給小朋友玩的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 這邊也有人守著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.63,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把一個東西忘在裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.13,0:12:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要把松井送到醫院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的腳傷成這樣 以後沒辦法再演哥梅拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.09,0:12:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說什麼哥梅拉 他現在連人都演不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.28,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這件案子解開了沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我還不知道兇手是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個兇手到底為什麼要特地跑到倉庫裡去攻擊松井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是他去拿那把兇器過來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好被松井先生看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些攝影用的小道具怎麼能拿來殺人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來這個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有可能那個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的麻醉槍不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你商量一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.19,0:13:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們現在就把松井帶到醫院去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在你們幾個裡面的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被我識破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要配合我聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把嘴巴動一動就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛 至少讓我表現一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道兇手是誰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.71,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你對大家說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手為什麼會從屋頂上消失呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是特殊攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種立體的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所看到的犯人其實都只是影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明在走廊上撞到兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還親眼看到他逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 剛才說的不算 不算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個很單純的詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.79,0:14:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些小朋友和阪口小姐的確看到了兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有在走廊轉彎之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後兇手有沒有上那個樓梯他們就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.25,0:14:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個樓梯上明明有留下腳印的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點配合我的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些腳印是兇手事先塗上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只塗在樓梯上而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本就沒有人到屋頂上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樓梯既然是通到屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就算沒有仔細確認也沒什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓梯上之所以只有留下腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是因為兇手利用哥梅拉的道具腳的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是走廊上有尾巴的印子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是樓梯上卻消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手站在這個塗著腳印的樓梯前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速脫掉道具服以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著和腳印相反方向下樓到下面的屋子裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.04,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再從那間屋子的窗戶將道具燒了以後再丟到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.44,0:15:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是兇手根本不知道佈景間到底放了什麼顏色的油漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會事先就把腳印給塗好了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對？ 安達先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那桶油漆是我在命案發生之前碰巧放在那邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個推理根本就是前後矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會前後矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.11,0:15:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阪口小姐與安達先生的證詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了包庇兇手的謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那桶油漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兇手在犯案之前放置好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是使用腳印的這個詭計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個知道兇手是誰囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.10,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過安達先生剛才只是順著阪口小姐的話說而己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以阪口小姐應該知道才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早在她和兇手在走廊上相撞的時候就看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 兇手到底是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是當然沒有到試映室看毛片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三上導演和松井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.82,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及原本在試映室中途離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪口小姐還有安達先生四個人中的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安達先生離開那裡的時候只有四分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能作案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.41,0:16:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小孩在一起目睹兇手背影的阪口小姐也是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就只有三上導演跟松井先生兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井先生的腳受了那麼嚴重的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三上導演還是我的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手是個大家意想不到的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？ 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要礙事 快到一邊去 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 快走…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是叫蒼蠅閃一邊去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 兇手是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是 松井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 松井老弟已經受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.23,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能穿著那身沉重的道具服逃走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他腳上的傷根本就不是在命案發生之前傷到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.39,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 難道說那個傷是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.73,0:17:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傷是在他行兇之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.36,0:17:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上道具服逃到樓下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.86,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又回到倉庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用另外一把刀自己弄的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了掩飾罪行的偽裝罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在命案發生之前小朋友就已經看過了他那個傷口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.63,0:17:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一些只是假血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是攝影棚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到假血當然不是問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些小朋友在看到那個傷口之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就跟在哥梅拉後面追到攝影棚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從倉庫到攝影棚之前的通道又只有一條而己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井先生到底又是在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超到小孩子的前面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.96,0:18:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要從倉庫對面走廊的入口出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以到攝影棚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在小孩子離開之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.43,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從那個地方到攝影棚的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到攝影棚之後再把道具服裝穿起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.79,0:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將龜井導演再用刀殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.08,0:18:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個詭計需要目擊者追著腳印才可以成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會把這些腳程比大人慢許多的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選為目擊者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他巧妙的運用了小孩子的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越叫他們別跟著去就越要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.99,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後之所以把道具服給燒掉目的是為了燒毀裡面的汗跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼松井先生就是兇手的證據呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.42,0:18:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井先生用來刺自己大腿的另外一把刀子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在攝影用的道具箱裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了那個地方之外沒有可以藏刀子之處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他腳已經受傷 動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是松井先生穿著的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件汗衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗衫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手穿著那身沉重的道具服用力跑的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他的汗衫應該會被汗水全部浸濕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.52,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在他汗衫上根本就沒有汗漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會有汗漬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他已經換過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這些孩子都可以為這一點作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為步美在倉庫裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經把果汁潑到松井先生的汗衫上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有看到果汁印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.68,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在哪裡換的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.13,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿被刺傷的話 不是不能動了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是你弄錯了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 好比說果汁是潑在地板上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你要再好好的想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 友美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子說得沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為全身流了汗才換了衣服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換下來的汗衫就在我的背包裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 快點去查一查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.40,0:20:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你為什麼要殺龜井製作人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是得到了拍下一部電影的機會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從一開始就不想拍那部片子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦子想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拍哥梅拉電影而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.81,0:20:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是最早表示不想拍哥梅拉的人不就是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全都是龜井製作人胡說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.03,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎麼會突然間擺出笑臉來鼓勵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來真正發現這些謊言的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.64,0:20:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個星期以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了就馬上跑去找龜井製作人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.79,0:20:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要以「哥梅拉最後大決戰」做標題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.39,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的大肆加以宣傳一番所以以後就不會有續集了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要過了一年以後大家馬上就會忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種用塑膠做出來的怪物 有什麼好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼不來找我商量呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法開口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你們幾個為了這個結局這麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不忍心開口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我完全不後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.01,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣的話 就永遠不會看到哥梅拉死亡的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我唯一後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓這些小孩子目擊到我殺人的那一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友美 這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的能夠從哥梅拉的背景看出是松井嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他一下子就消失掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.99,0:21:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.47,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算沒有看到裡面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光看他的動作我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.07,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我跟松井一起同甘共苦了十年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的好夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.65,0:23:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.86,0:23:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉還是順利的在電影院上演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.51,0:23:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有拍到的最後一個畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利用之前曾經播過的帶子加以合成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哥梅拉死亡一幕剪掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.04,0:23:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉就這樣永遠活在銀幕裡和觀眾的心目中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為內容精彩又充滿了爆發力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.25,0:23:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得有很多的觀眾都來觀看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.20,0:23:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.42,0:23:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥梅拉在電影院裡面回蕩不停的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們聽來卻充滿了無限淒涼的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.64,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺岡先生跟松山先生在搶奪手槍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.92,0:23:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手槍走火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.03,0:23:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意外嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.32,0:23:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 關於昨天的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.10,0:23:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事情我們還沒有向媒體記者披露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.26,0:24:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們在槍支上面發現第三人的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.51,0:24:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個第三個指紋到底是誰的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.33,0:24:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那把手槍的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我所推理出來的人的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.42,0:24:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.74,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3個指紋殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.55,0:24:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影帶盒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.24,0:24:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也是很獨特的事件喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.98,0:24:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週敬請期待
